  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 46e03a19f8e5e124dad137a0f14696cc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialogue Day 1 Faction Member
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - "Hey\u2026 You"
  - "You\u2019re the dad of the towns \u201Coh soooo beloved\u201D daughter, aren\u2019t
    you?"
  - "And you\u2019re sitting here slaving away for those government fucks, what an
    embarrassment."
  - "You: \u2026I\u2019m sorry, I don\u2019t quite understand what you\u2019re saying?"
  - "Oh, whoever could have guessed? The pawn doesn\u2019t understand why someone
    would dislike the amazing government, they\u2019ve never done him wrong have
    they?"
  - "Ignorant fucks like you piss me off. We\u2019re the same age\u2026 you remember
    that day\u2026. maybe not fully, but well enough. "
  - "That day they \u201Csaved us\u201D from the government that \u201Ckidnapped
    our parents\u201D. There\u2019s more to that truth, is there not? YOU KNOW SOMETHING
    ELSE HAPPENED THAT DAY, DON\u2019T YOU?"
  - "YOU DON\u2019T TRULY TRUST THEM EITHER, DO YOU!?!?"
  - 'You: ...'
  - "Would you look at that, another one that\u2019s too afraid to admit it"
  - "Don\u2019t know why I bother, some idiots are beyond saving."
